                <p><label type="entry">VERTEX</label> denotes the crown of the head. Hence vertex is
                    also used figuratively for the top of other things; thus we say, the vertex of a
                    cone, pyramid, &amp;c.</p>
                <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Vertex</hi> is also used in <hi rend="italic">Astronomy</hi>
                    for the point of the heaven directly over our heads, properly called the <hi
                        rend="italic">zenith.</hi></p>
            </div>
